Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.02,0:01:41.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm Kagome Higurashi, a ninth grader.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:44.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}My family are caretakers of\na very old, historic shrine...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.86,0:01:47.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and I've led a very normal life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.43,0:01:50.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But on my fifteenth birthday,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.37,0:01:53.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was dragged into the civil war period...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.24,0:01:55.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}by a demon who suddenly appeared\nfrom the old shrine well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.31,0:02:00.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here, countless demons\nwishing to increase their power...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.48,0:02:02.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}search for the Sacred Jewel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.48,0:02:06.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is where I met a half-demon\nnamed Inuyasha.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.92,0:02:12.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha wants the Sacred Jewel\nto become a full-fledged demon...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.63,0:02:20.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ever since, we've traveled together\nfrom place to place...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.53,0:02:23.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}in search of Sacred Jewel Shards which\nare scattered throughout the country.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:27.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}We've fought many demons in our search\nfor the Sacred Jewel Shards,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.71,0:02:29.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}but we've also made friends\nalong the way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.64,0:02:34.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shippo is a very cute fox demon child.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:38.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He always tries so hard and helps us\nwith his fox magic.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.19,0:02:42.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miroku is a monk.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.62,0:02:44.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}His Wind Tunnel, inflicted on his palm\nby Naraku's curse,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.99,0:02:47.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}has the power to suck anything\ninto it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.70,0:02:51.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's a dependable person, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.64,0:02:58.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sango is the last survivor of a\n{\i1}tribe of demon slayers.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.31,0:03:02.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her mission is to destroy Naraku\nto avenge her tribe...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.18,0:03:04.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and so, she has been traveling with us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.78,0:03:09.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The worst one is that Naraku!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.45,0:03:14.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Without sullying his hands, he resorts to\ndirty tricks and sets sneaky traps...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.35,0:03:16.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A despicable beast!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.82,0:03:19.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's been steadily collecting the\NShikon Jewel Shards,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.19,0:03:21.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}growing more and more powerful.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.20,0:03:26.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But we'll pool our strength together,\nand someday, we'll get rid of him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.54,0:03:32.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll seek out Naraku's castle\nand destroy him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.14,0:03:36.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our journey continues!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.62,0:03:52.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry to trouble you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.49,0:03:53.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I felt this sudden pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:56.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't mention it. It's all part\nof a monk's duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.40,0:03:58.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:03:59.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.43,0:04:01.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yup, again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.70,0:04:04.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How do you feel now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:08.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.\NI feel much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.78,0:04:10.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But you shouldn't overexert yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.68,0:04:12.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:15.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Really?\NWell, I'm glad then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.75,0:04:17.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.85,0:04:18.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.12,0:04:21.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Will you bear my child?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.12,0:04:23.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.66,0:04:24.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:26.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yup, again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.59,0:04:29.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll be off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.46,0:04:30.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.47,0:04:34.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.53,0:04:37.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why do you always come on\nto pretty girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.74,0:04:41.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's just that I cannot ignore\na girl in distress.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.94,0:04:42.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.98,0:04:45.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Anyway, we must hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:47.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're the one who kept us waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.78,0:04:50.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.22,0:04:57.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh! Say, how about taking a short break?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.36,0:04:59.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That sounds nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.53,0:05:02.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Huh?\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.96,0:05:04.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Miroku?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.76,0:05:08.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My travel funds... my money... is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:09.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.47,0:05:11.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sure I had it this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.54,0:05:13.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It must've been that woman\nat the roadside!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.67,0:05:14.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She was a pickpocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.17,0:05:15.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.28,0:05:20.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No wonder she didn't go bonkers when\nyou stroked her butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.61,0:05:22.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What have I done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.32,0:05:23.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,C'mon! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.27,0:05:41.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say! Where's Miroku?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.27,0:05:43.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What happened to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.70,0:05:46.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He was lagging behind a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.44,0:05:50.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe he's depressed\nafter getting robbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.54,0:05:51.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll go check.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.92,0:05:57.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.82,0:05:59.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.02,0:06:02.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No. Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.06,0:06:04.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ho... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.12,0:06:08.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're all worried sick and\nwe don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.39,0:06:10.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, there's no need to worry\nany longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.70,0:06:13.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Monk?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.67,0:06:16.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Well... nothing... yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.60,0:06:21.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The men who went into the mountain\nhaven't returned?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.67,0:06:25.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're sure they've been captured\nby demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:26.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.31,0:06:29.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Saving people for free again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.82,0:06:31.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Come on, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.92,0:06:33.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.25,0:06:34.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.75,0:06:37.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please... save my husband!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.22,0:06:40.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You have a husband, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.16,0:06:40.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:47.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess it's very lonely without\nyour husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.70,0:06:50.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh please, Monk, lend us\nyour power.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.60,0:06:53.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right. We shall go and\nfree your men.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.11,0:06:56.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:06:58.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Got that, Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.88,0:07:02.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, I'm the one that has to\ndeliver the finishing blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:03.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.92,0:07:10.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now then, let us go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.46,0:07:13.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please be very careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.09,0:07:18.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,According to rumors,\nthe demon is a beautiful woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.13,0:07:21.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I shall go alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.77,0:07:30.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But why did Miroku go off by himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:32.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He probably wants to be alone\nwith the beautiful demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.78,0:07:35.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He never learns, does he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.28,0:07:39.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango, are you following him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.99,0:07:41.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.62,0:07:46.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Leave that womanizing monk and\nhe'll be the one who gets bewitched.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.43,0:07:47.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Come on, Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.73,0:07:52.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say, Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.87,0:07:53.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.77,0:07:55.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've been thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.30,0:07:58.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm willing to bet that Sango has\nfeelings for Miroku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.74,0:08:00.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? What're you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.84,0:08:03.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Haven't you noticed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.28,0:08:03.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.18,0:08:06.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I sorta had an inkling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:07.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.75,0:08:09.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're so dense!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.75,0:08:10.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.98,0:08:14.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You've seen how Sango gets upset\nwhen Miroku strokes her buns.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.25,0:08:18.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Listen... Women are creatures that\ncherish mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.62,0:08:20.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's "mood"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.03,0:08:21.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:24.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Err... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.03,0:08:28.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Anyway, Sango likes Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:31.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.81,0:08:37.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! What're you sighing for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.81,0:08:38.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.78,0:08:41.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you get it? We're going to\ndestroy a demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.88,0:08:42.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.12,0:08:44.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,According to the villagers,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.82,0:08:50.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,long ago, defeated soldiers escaped\ndeep into this mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.99,0:08:54.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And there was a princess among them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:58.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But all the men who protected her died.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.50,0:09:01.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And eventually, the princess also died.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.00,0:09:02.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.97,0:09:06.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And her bitterness turned her\ninto a demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.27,0:09:08.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.57,0:09:09.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.08,0:09:13.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess that's how women are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.31,0:09:15.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:17.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well... women certainly are persistent,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.72,0:09:22.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,prone to jealousy and bursts of anger,\nand hatred... I've known so many like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:24.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're so experienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.89,0:09:28.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,However, even I don't know what kind\nof demon is created...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.23,0:09:32.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,from the bitterness of a princess who\ndies a lonely death.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.00,0:09:34.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,l just have to see with my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:38.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Still, why decide to go alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.10,0:09:39.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well... I have my reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.38,0:09:43.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can you see it, Sango?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.08,0:09:44.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.05,0:09:47.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's the entrance to the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.28,0:09:50.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Furthermore, this barrier...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.82,0:09:54.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,...seems easy to enter,\nbut difficult to exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.02,0:09:55.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.12,0:10:00.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Put it on. It may prove helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.96,0:10:01.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.73,0:10:06.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let us go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.57,0:10:08.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.48,0:10:22.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miroku! Easy to enter?\NYou must've been kidding!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.75,0:10:23.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Such strong resistance!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.22,0:10:26.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.32,0:10:30.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.06,0:10:36.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:39.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where are you, Sango?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.77,0:10:42.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We've been separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.67,0:10:48.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.14,0:10:51.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.18,0:10:57.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why are you here so deep\nin this mountain?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.65,0:11:00.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A demon... this girl?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.52,0:11:04.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, whatever the reason,\ncome to the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.70,0:11:14.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!\NWhere are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.83,0:11:16.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.27,0:11:22.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demons?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.05,0:11:31.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}People...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.29,0:11:35.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Old men... all of them!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.39,0:11:39.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Umm... Old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.63,0:11:40.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ehh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.56,0:11:43.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.60,0:11:45.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I... ain't an old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.30,0:11:48.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Y-You are old.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.73,0:11:50.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I ain't old!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.24,0:11:52.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I ain't old either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.30,0:11:54.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ain't one either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.44,0:11:56.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I ain't an old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:57.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ain't old!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.91,0:11:59.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ain't an old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:04.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're all not... old?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.12,0:12:08.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku's the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.99,0:12:11.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder how he feels about Sango?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:14.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Any woman will do for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.23,0:12:18.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I think Sango is a special case.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.73,0:12:21.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, he does try to feel up Sango's\nbutt often enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.10,0:12:24.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,C'mon! I don't mean it like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.87,0:12:27.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm tired of all this talk.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.07,0:12:32.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? You're the men who disappeared\nfrom the village?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.58,0:12:34.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:36.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was like a dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.95,0:12:44.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was lost and in trouble when the\nmost beautiful princess appeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.46,0:12:49.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She brought me to a magnificent villa\nand I had such a grand time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.36,0:12:51.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Grand time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.13,0:12:53.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was grand...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.97,0:12:56.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah... It sure was grand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.87,0:13:01.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then when we snapped out of it,\nwe were like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:06.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The demon sucked the life spirit,\nthe youth, out of the men.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:11.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You survived the war?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.92,0:13:12.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.72,0:13:15.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And my vassals have all died.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.89,0:13:20.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am alone... and very lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.46,0:13:21.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How tragic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.43,0:13:23.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Monk...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.70,0:13:24.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.50,0:13:26.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am unable to\nleave this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.13,0:13:29.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Will you spend at least the night\nwith me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.50,0:13:32.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is that your wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.04,0:13:37.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Monk... Please look\ninto my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.31,0:13:43.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Anyway, when the princess gazed\nat you with those eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.18,0:13:49.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was mesmerized and nothing\nmattered anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.29,0:13:51.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara, you stay close to\nthese people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.99,0:13:58.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cripes! That womanizing monk\nwill fall right into her trap!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.97,0:14:01.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.80,0:14:02.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh Monk!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.54,0:14:09.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miroku!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.85,0:14:15.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stay alive until I get there!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.32,0:14:19.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miroku!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.33,0:14:33.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why that...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.47,0:14:36.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wake up, you lecherous monk!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.37,0:14:37.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A woman's voice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.04,0:14:41.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.37,0:15:10.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.90,0:15:13.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You will not interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.61,0:15:16.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It cannot see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.41,0:15:17.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.98,0:15:19.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait, Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.68,0:15:22.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku! Weren't you bewitched?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:27.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't speak! If you remain quiet,\nit won't know where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:31.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see! It's the power of the beads\nthat Miroku gave me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.56,0:15:35.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But why isn't he destroying the demon?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.23,0:15:38.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The true form of the demon is\na female coyote.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.47,0:15:42.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Become part of my power!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.00,0:15:45.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.90,0:15:46.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.34,0:15:51.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wanted to take care of this\nquietly, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.11,0:15:56.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Princess! You'll have to endure\na bit of pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.58,0:15:57.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.12,0:15:59.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please bear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.00,0:16:16.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A princess inside the demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.84,0:16:20.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:34.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.32,0:16:38.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn monk!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:42.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I shall show no mercy now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.30,0:16:47.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.04,0:16:54.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Give back the princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.87,0:16:56.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.84,0:16:57.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.01,0:16:59.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hiraikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.71,0:17:02.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.02,0:17:06.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.75,0:17:08.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.93,0:17:14.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.29,0:17:41.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}My power...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.79,0:17:47.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The demon power l gathered...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.37,0:17:58.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku... What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.41,0:18:02.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was very rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.41,0:18:04.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Monk...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.38,0:18:11.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You were alone for so long.\NIt must've been lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.92,0:18:17.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, because I was so weak-hearted,\NI fell victim to a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.12,0:18:22.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You'll be all right now.\NI'll take you to the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.70,0:18:25.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.51,0:18:40.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.55,0:18:44.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That is her soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.95,0:18:47.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She died all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.25,0:18:49.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rather than bitterness...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.72,0:18:52.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,it was loneliness that kept her\nfrom finding peace in death.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.93,0:18:57.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The demon coyote stole the\nprincess' body and soul,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.53,0:18:59.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,then impersonated her to lure men...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.70,0:19:03.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and sucked out their youth\nto gain strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.17,0:19:11.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've placed the princess' ashes\nin this grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.31,0:19:16.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you offer prayers, I'm sure\nshe will watch over the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.62,0:19:18.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.85,0:19:21.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You brought our men back\nhome to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.59,0:19:24.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was like a beautiful dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.26,0:19:25.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll say.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.89,0:19:28.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.39,0:19:29.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.36,0:19:31.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did something happen\nin that mountain?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:34.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango has seemed awfully depressed\nsince coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.93,0:19:38.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well... I don't know what it could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.01,0:19:45.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I feel like such a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.28,0:19:49.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.75,0:19:53.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.39,0:19:58.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku, you really didn't need me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.32,0:20:03.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No such thing! You're the one\nwho destroyed the demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.70,0:20:05.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Only because you helped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.30,0:20:08.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, I relied on your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.40,0:20:11.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Because I believed in your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.57,0:20:15.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're imagining things!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.84,0:20:18.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango wouldn't fall in love\nwith that lecher!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.94,0:20:21.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why not? Look at that mood!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:23.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So what is "mood" anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.52,0:20:29.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango, you came because you were\nworried for my safety, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.86,0:20:34.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well... that's... of course, I was worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.23,0:20:38.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When it comes to women,\nyou don't discriminate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:41.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was sure you'd get into trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.60,0:20:43.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.47,0:20:49.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,l just couldn't ignore a woman\nwho might be grieving.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.08,0:20:53.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not jealous or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.15,0:21:01.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's what you call "mood."\NMood!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.39,0:21:03.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,More than any woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.19,0:21:08.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your concern for me\nmakes me happiest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.63,0:21:13.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! What're you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.03,0:21:16.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh no! What'll I do?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.07,0:21:18.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go for it, Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.44,0:21:20.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.05,0:21:32.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That hand...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.65,0:21:36.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why not touch my shoulders...\nor somewhere more...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.29,0:21:40.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't you know anything else!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.03,0:21:49.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well... She seemed to be silently\nbegging me to touch her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.60,0:21:50.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.40,0:21:52.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rather than women themselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.64,0:21:54.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you need to brush up on knowing\nwomen's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.34,0:21:57.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,See? Didn't I tell you\nthat you're all wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.74,0:21:58.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.38,0:22:01.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Boy, such a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.69,0:22:08.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Better fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.52,0:23:50.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?! Going back home again?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.22,0:23:52.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you like "tests" that much, Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.66,0:23:55.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, it can't be helped.\NI have things I need to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.66,0:23:58.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is this creepy-looking fruit?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.36,0:24:00.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A fruit with a human face from Togenkyo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.27,0:24:01.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you kidding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.60,0:24:04.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Using humans to make\nanti-aging potions?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.70,0:24:06.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And you call yourself a sage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.51,0:24:11.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"Fateful Night in Togenkyo, Part l"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.14,0:24:14.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! The moon is disappearing!
